metadata.name: Entelechy 1
metadata.description:
Black wood veins with 17820 particles, 320x320x2 pixels, 180 frames, 16 colors

Entelechy (realisation of potential) is an ongoing research of flow-forms found in nature. Each piece is based on different materials.

According to theories all the way from Tao to Goethe the realisation of supreme potential of a thing, can be achieved by allowing the nature of the thing to define our path around it. Just by being sensitive enough to flow around the subject and adopt to its nature.
